### Register a new user
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "ivan_petrenko",
  "password": "strongpassword",
  "name": "Іван"
}

### Login user
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "ivan_petrenko",
  "password": "strongpassword"
}

### Refresh tokens from cookie or body
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### Get current profile
GET http://localhost:3000/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Logout current user
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Create announcement with auth
POST http://localhost:3000/announcements
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

Продам ноутбук ASUS
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

Відмінний стан, 16GB RAM, SSD 512GB
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="price"

18000
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="category"

sale
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="contactInfo"

0991234567
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Create announcement with photo
POST http://localhost:3000/announcements
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

Продам велосипед
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

Trek у відмінному стані
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="price"

8500
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="category"

sale
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="contactInfo"

veloman@gmail.com
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="bike.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./path/to/bike.jpg
--boundary--

### Create announcement without auth
POST http://localhost:3000/announcements
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Продам ноутбук ASUS",
  "description": "Відмінний стан, 16GB RAM, SSD 512GB",
  "price": 18000,
  "category": "sale",
  "contactInfo": "0991234567"
}

### Update someone else's announcement
PATCH http://localhost:3000/announcements/1
Authorization: Bearer {{otherAccessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 17000
}

### Delete someone else's announcement
DELETE http://localhost:3000/announcements/1
Authorization: Bearer {{otherAccessToken}}
